    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make horse owners legally responsible for removing manure from public areas",
        "additional_details": "We ask the Government to extend dog fouling laws to horses or create a new law requiring all horse owners and equine businesses to remove manure from public areas.",
        "background": "Require horse owners and equine businesses to clean up horse manure in public areas by extending dog fouling laws or creating a new law. ",
